Add support to handle REP/REPNE prefixes to the x86-64 validator.

This change does:

(1) Defines which instructions allow REP/REPNE prefixes.
(2) Only validates instructions with allowable REP/REPNE prefixes.
(3) Change instructions allowing REP/REPNE prefixes to the use
    the new notation for modeling instructions.
(4) Test that the validator flags REP/REPNE prefixes when appropriate.
(5) Fix bug in scas instructions (refers to wrong segment register pair).

BUG=http://code.google.com/p/nativeclient/issues/detail?id=930

